subject: Fix reserved keyword 'eval' in destructuring assignment
body:
The compliance-analyzer.js was using 'eval' as a variable name in a
destructuring assignment, which is a reserved JavaScript keyword and
causes a SyntaxError. Renamed to 'evaluation'.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
title: Fix reserved keyword 'eval' in destructuring assignment
